        "position": 1,
        "title": "Can fit 2 smaller sized cats!",
        "text": "I was able to take both my cats (they are about 10-15lbs each) in this carrier and it was pretty sturdy. I used alaska airlines and sat near the back (near the bathroom) in case I had to clean up cat urine from the long flight. Sitting on the edge seat gave me room to keep the popped out mesh part open and the kitties were able to relax with some medication involved. The strap was really nice too because I could put it around my neck and hold it like a big belly when I needed to wear my carry on backpack. The pockets I kept wet wipes for accidents,pee pads, and treats. When I introduced my cats to the removable cushion at home they were laying on it so it must be comfortable for them. The inside cushion fabric is machine washable too. This is going to be my cat carrier from now on.",
        "rating": 5,
        "date": "March 27, 2026",
        "author": "The Wasons",
        "author_link": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AHWIRUIT4PUZDJI5XT6R56WT56DQ",
        "author_image": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/2ddb2414-d3b6-4c64-8868-399291c23575._CR0%2C0%2C500%2C500_SX460_.jpeg",
