        "position": 2,
        "title": "A must for airplane travel",
        "text": "Moved to Hawaii and was worried about my cat fitting as she's pretty large., 14 lb cat.Whole it was still stressful because she has anxiety, this was absolutely great because it proved to be scratch and bite proof.It also helped that the sides folded out for more room.I did buy the pee pads just in case, but she never made one accident.6 hours, 12 hour lay over, then another 6 hours.Definitely recommend for flying, it went through with zero issues ! Great price, easy to assemble",
